'Yan majalisar dokokin Wales ba sa son su zama 'yan fashi.
Wasu daga cikin mambobin Majalisar Dokokin kasar sun nuna rashin jin daɗi game da shawarar da aka ba su don karɓar sunan MWP (daga Turanci Member of the Welsh Parliament  memba na Majalisar Wales).
Wannan matsala ta shafi shirin canza sunan Majalisar zuwa Majalisar Wales.
'Yan majalisa daga jam'iyyun siyasa daban-daban suna damuwa da yiwuwar wargi da wannan gajerar kalma.
Wani ɗan jam'iyyar Labour, yana bayyana ra'ayin jam'iyyarsa, ya nuna damuwa game da sabon gajerun kalmomi  da aka rubuta Twp da Pwp.
Ga masu karatu da ba 'yan Wales ba: a yaren Welsh, twp yana nufin maƙwabci, kuma pwp  kakka.
A cewar wani dan majalisa daga jam'iyyar Wales, kungiyarsa ba ta gamsu ba kuma ta ba da wasu zaɓuɓɓuka.
Wakilan jam'iyyar masu ra'ayin mazan jiya ba su da wata matsala game da sabon gajerun kalmomi, amma suna lura cewa MWP yana kusa da rubutun Muppet (muppets).
A wannan yanayin, ana furta w a yaren Welsh kamar yadda ake furta u a yaren Yorkshire.
Kwamitin Majalisar, wanda a halin yanzu yake aiki da dokar sauya suna, ya yi wannan sanarwa: Dokar karshe game da yadda za a kira 'yan majalisa, ba shakka, zai kasance a gare su.
Dokar Gudanar da Wales ta 2017 ta ba da izinin Majalisar Wakilai ta Wales ta canza sunanta.
A watan Yuni, Kwamitin ya wallafa sakamakon binciken da aka yi game da zaɓuɓɓukan da aka ba da shawarar, wanda ya nuna cewa zaɓin 'Majalisar Wales' maimakon 'Majalisar' ya sami goyon baya sosai a tsakanin mazauna.
Game da sunan mambobin Majalisar, Kwamitin ya fi son zaɓin Mambobin Majalisar Wales (Welsh Parliament Members, ko WMP), yayin da zaɓin MWP ya sami goyon baya mafi yawa daga jama'a.
A cewarsa, 'yan majalisa suna da wasu shawarwari, amma shugaban majalisar, Elina Jones, ba za ta samu sauki ba wajen samar da wani tsari da zai gamsar da kowa.
Dokokin gyare-gyare za su hada da wasu gyare-gyare ga tsarin aikin Majalisar, ciki har da sababbin dokoki game da yanke wa mambobin Majalisar da kuma tsarin tsarin kwamitin.
'Yan majalisa za su yi zabe a kan sunan da za a ba su a lokacin da za a yi muhawara kan dokar.
