A California, wani kifi mai suna shark ya ji wa wani ɗan shekara 13 rauni a ruwa
Rahotanni sun ce a ranar Asabar, ranar farko ta farautar lobster, wani dan wasan ruwa dan shekara 13 ya ji rauni a jikinsa bayan da wani kifi ya kai masa hari.
An kai harin ne da misalin karfe 7 na safiyar yau kusa da bakin rairayin bakin teku na Beacon Beach a Encinitas.
A wata hira da tashar KSWB-TV ta San Diego, Chad Hammel ya ce a safiyar Asabar din da ya yi ruwa tare da abokansa, bayan kusan rabin sa'a sai ya ji kukan yaron yana neman taimako, sai suka hau jirgin ruwa zuwa wurin da aka kai harin kuma suka ceto yaron daga cikin ruwan.
A cewar Hummel, da farko ya yi tunanin cewa yaron yana farin ciki sosai da kama lobster, amma da sauri ya fahimci cewa yana ihu "An cije ni!"
An cije ni!
Da ya kai wurin mai ruwan, Hammel ya lura cewa fatar jikinsa ta tsage gaba ɗaya.
"Na yi ihu na ce wa kowa ya fito daga cikin ruwa, 'Shark yana nan!' " in ji Hummel.
An kai yaron zuwa asibitin yara na Reddy (San Diego); an kiyasta yanayinsa a matsayin mai tsanani.
Ba a san irin kifin da ya kai wa matashin hari ba.
