Gasar zaben Trump a West Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump ya fara taron neman zaben a garin Wheeling na jihar West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne na farko daga cikin tarurruka biyar da Trump zai yi a mako mai zuwa, ciki har da ziyarar da zai kai ga Tennessee da Mississippi.
Tun da aka jinkirta zaben shugaban kasa, Trump na neman samun goyon baya a zaben da ake yi a tsakiyar shekara, saboda 'yan Republican na iya rasa iko a majalisar idan aka yi zaben a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne za a yi taron Trump a yammacin Virginia kuma ta yaya za a iya kallon taron a kan layi?
Za a gana da Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia, da karfe 7 na yammacin yamma a yau Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon ganawar Trump da masu jefa kuri'a a West Virginia ta yanar gizo ta hanyar watsa shirye-shiryen kai tsaye a YouTube.
Ana sa ran Trump zai yi jawabi a zaman da za a yi a wannan makon kan yadda zai zabi Brett Kavanaugh a matsayin babban alkalin kotun, wanda ya janyo cece-kuce da yawa saboda zargin cin zarafin da aka yi wa Kavanaugh, kuma za a dage zaben da aka shirya a majalisar dattijai har zuwa mako guda yayin da FBI ke gudanar da bincike.
Amma babban burin wannan kamfen shi ne taimaka wa 'yan Republican da za su fafata a zaben watan Nuwamba su kara saurin fafatawa.
A sakamakon haka, yakin neman zaben shugaban kasar Trump ya yi niyyar ganin cewa ganawar da za a yi a mako mai zuwa za ta taimaka wajen kara samun masu ba da agaji da magoya baya yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da kuma kara yawan rinjaye a majalisar dattawa da majalisar wakilai.
"Sarrafa majalisar dokoki yana da matukar muhimmanci ga ajandar shugaban kasa, don haka ya kamata ya ziyarci jihohi da dama kamar yadda zai yiwu, saboda muna shiga cikin lokacin yakin neman zabe", in ji mai magana da yawun yakin neman zaben Trump, wanda ya ƙi bayyana sunansa, in ji Reuters.
Taron da aka shirya a Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling a yau zai iya jawo hankalin magoya baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania, kuma zai iya jan hankalin kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh, West Virginia Metro News ta ruwaito.
Ziyarar Trump zuwa West Virginia a wannan Asabar ita ce ziyara ta biyu da ya kai jihar a cikin wata guda, inda ya samu kashi 40 cikin dari a shekarar 2016.
Trump yana kokarin taimakawa dan takarar majalisar dattijai na West Virginia, Patrick Morrissey, wanda ke baya a sakamakon binciken.
"Gaskiyar cewa shugaban kasa ya zo domin ya fara samun nasara a zaben shugaban kasa, ba alama ce mai kyau ba ga Morris", in ji Simon Heather, masanin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia.
