Mene ne bikin 'yan ƙasa na duniya kuma shin ya yi wani abu don rage talauci?
A wannan Asabar a birnin New York, za a yi bikin Global Citizen Festival  wani biki na kiɗa na shekara-shekara wanda ke nuna manyan taurari tare da irin wannan manufa  kawo ƙarshen talauci a duniya.
A shekara ta bakwai, dubban mutane sun yi ta zuwa babban filin shakatawa na Central Park don sauraron waƙoƙin Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes, da kuma bayyana ainihin manufar taron: kawar da talauci ta 2030.
Bikin 'yan ƙasa na duniya, wanda aka ƙaddamar a shekara ta 2012, ci gaba ne na aikin yaki da talauci na duniya wanda ƙungiyar masu kare hakkin ɗan adam ta duniya ke gudanarwa, wanda ke fatan kawo ƙarshen talauci ta hanyar ƙara yawan mutanen da ke fafutukar yaƙar ta.
Don samun tikiti kyauta don taron (idan ba ku da shirye-shiryen biyan kuɗin VIP), dole ne ku shiga aikin sa kai ko aika imel zuwa shugaban duniya, yin kira ta waya ko yin wani abu ko wasu ayyuka masu mahimmanci don taimakawa wayar da kan jama'a game da burin ku na kawar da talauci.
Amma yaya nasarar da bikin 'yan ƙasa na duniya ya samu a cikin shekaru 12 da suka gabata wajen cimma burinsa?
Shin wannan ra'ayin na ba wa mutane kyautar halartar wani biki na kyauta yana tabbatar da 'yan kasar su nemi kira zuwa aiki, ko kuma wani misali ne na abin da ake kira "tambaya" inda mutane ke gaskanta cewa suna kawo canji ta hanyar sanya hannu kan takarda kan layi ko aika saƙonni a Twitter?
Masu shirya bikin Global Citizen sun ce tun daga shekarar 2011, an yi rijistar ayyuka sama da miliyan 19 da magoya bayansa suka gudanar, wadanda ke bin manufofi daban-daban.
An ambaci cewa saboda waɗannan ayyukan shugabannin duniya sun yi alkawarin ba da sama da dala biliyan 37 na Amurka, wanda ya kamata ya shafi rayuwar mutane sama da biliyan 2.25 nan da shekarar 2030.
A farkon 2018, kungiyar ta bayyana alkawura 390 da kuma sanarwar da aka yi sakamakon ayyukanta, aƙalla dala biliyan 10 daga cikinsu an riga an biya ko an tara su.
Ƙungiyar ta ce, kusan mutane miliyan 649 ne suka amfana daga wannan tallafin.
