Sanata Elizabeth Warren daga jihar Massachusetts ta ce a ranar Asabar za ta yi nazari sosai kan yiwuwar tsayawa takarar shugaban kasa bayan zaben wucin gadi.
A wani taron majalisar dattijai a Holyoke, Massachusetts, Warren ta tabbatar da cewa za ta yi tunanin shiga cikin zaben.
"Lokaci ya yi da mata za su je Washington su gyara gwamnatinmu da ta lalace, kuma hakan na bukatar mace a kan kujerar", in ji Warren The Hill.
Bayan ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba, zan yi la'akari da yiwuwar tsayawa takarar shugaban kasa.
Warren ta ce shugaban Amurka Donald Trump yana kan hanyar da ba ta dace ba.
"Ina matukar damuwa da abin da Donald Trump ke yi wa dimokiradiyarmu", in ji ta.
Warren ya kasance mai sukar Trump da kuma dan takararsa na Kotun Koli Brett Kavanaugh.
