A ranar Laraba, shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi amfani da shafin Des Moines Register China Daily, babban jaridar kasuwanci a jihar Iowa, wajen zargin kasar Sin da kokarin tsoma baki a zaben majalisar dokokin Amurka da za a yi a ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba.
