Girgizar Kasa da Tsunami a Indonesiya
A kalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a girgizar kasa da tsunami da ta afkawa birnin Palau na kasar Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, kuma ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu, a cewar jami'ai.
Saboda rashin sadarwa, masu aikin ceto ba za su iya samun wani bayani daga Donggal ba, wani yanki da ke arewacin Palau, wanda ya fi kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasar mai karfin awo 7.5.
An kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 daga Palau.
Ga wasu abubuwa masu muhimmanci game da Palau da Donggala da ke tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu  babban birnin lardin Tsakiyar Sulawesi ne, wanda ke ƙarshen wani ɗan ƙaramin bakin teku a yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da yawan jama'a 379,800 (bayanai na 2017).
A lokacin da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka auku, birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafuwarsa.
Donggala  wani yanki ne da ke da nisan kilomita 300 (180 miles) a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
Gundumar, yanki ne na yanki wanda ya fi ƙarami a lardin, a cikin 2017 yana da mazauna 299,200.
Kifi da noma sune tushen tattalin arzikin lardin Tsakiyar Sulawesi, musamman yankin Donggala da ke bakin teku.
Har ila yau, hakar nickel yana da mahimmanci ga tattalin arzikin lardin, amma an fi mayar da hankali ne a Morali, a gefen tekun Sulawesi.
Hukumar Kula da Bala'i ta ƙasar Indonesia ta ce, a cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige, an yi wasu guguwa da suka halaka Palau da Donggala.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya halaka ɗaruruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Tsunami kuma ya faru a yammacin Donggala a shekara ta 1996, wanda ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin da ake kira Pacific Ring of Fire kuma tana fama da girgizar ƙasa sosai.
Ga wasu manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh na Indonesia a arewacin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga Disamba ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya afku a kasashe 14, wanda ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: Ƙarƙashin ƙasa mai ƙarfi ya afku a yammacin gabar Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Mutane da yawa sun mutu a tsibirin Nias da ke bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 6.8 ta afku a kudancin Java, tsibiri mafi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, ta haifar da tsunami da ta afku a gabar teku ta kudu, wanda ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: An yi wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.6 a birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin Yammacin Sumatra.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 ta auku a tsibirin Mentawai da ke bakin tekun Sumatra, ta haddasa tsunami mai tsayin mita 10, wanda ya lalata ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane kusan 300.
2016: Wani mummunar girgizar kasa ta afkawa gundumar Pidi-Jaya a Aceh, ta haifar da lalacewa da firgici yayin da mutane ke tunawa da girgizar kasa da tsunami mai lalacewa a shekarar 2004.
Amma mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu a lokacin da gine-ginen suka rushe.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok na Indonesia, ta kashe mutane sama da 500, galibi a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta bar dubban masu yawon bude ido a ƙarƙashin kango.
