Ofishin lauyoyin tarayya na son yankewa wani wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci a New York hukuncin kisa.
Ofishin lauya na tarayya a New York na neman hukuncin kisa ga Saifullo Saipov, wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci a New York wanda ya kashe mutane takwas - hukuncin da ba a saba yi ba ga wani laifi na tarayya wanda ba a yi amfani da shi ba a jihar tun 1953.
A watan Oktoba, Saipov, mai shekara 30, ya yi hayar wata babbar mota ta Home Depot don kai hari a kan hanyar keke a kan hanyar West Side a Lower Manhattan, yana kashe masu tafiya da keke.
Don tabbatar da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara za su tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya "da gangan" ya kashe mutane takwas kuma ya "da gangan" ya yi mummunan rauni, a cewar sanarwar niyyar neman hukuncin kisa da aka gabatar a gundumar kudu ta New York.
A cewar takardun kotu, za a iya yanke hukuncin kisa a kan waɗannan zarge-zarge biyu.
Makonni bayan harin, wata babbar kotun tarayya ta yanke wa Saipov hukuncin kisa mai dauke da abubuwa 22, wanda ya hada da laifuka takwas na kisan kai da ake amfani da su a kotun tarayya a shari'ar aikata laifuka, da kuma laifuka na amfani da tashin hankali da lalata motoci.
A cewar masu gabatar da kara, harin ya kasance ainihin da aka tsara da gangan, Saipov ya aiwatar da shi, kamar yadda aka bayyana, ainihin, zalunci da kuma aikata laifi.
Saifulla Habibullayevich Saipov ya yi wa dangin Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Lora Decad, Darren Drake, Ariel Erli, Ernan Ferrucci, Ernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damian Pagnocco rauni, ya yi wa dangin su lahani, ya kuma yi wa dangin su lahani, in ji sanarwar.
Mutum biyar da suka mutu 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
Shekara goma ke nan da aka yanke hukuncin kisa a gundumar kudu ta birnin New York.
A watan Satumbar 2009, an yanke wa wanda ake tuhuma Khalid Barnes hukuncin kisa kan kisan wasu dillalan miyagun kwayoyi biyu, amma a karshe an yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai da rai.
An yi amfani da hukuncin kisa a cikin shari'ar tarayya a New York a shekarar 1953 a kan Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata da aka kashe don yin tawaye ga Tarayyar Soviet a lokacin Cold War shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
An kashe Rosenbergs da amfani da kujera ta lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
