An samu ɓarkewar cutar a cikin nisan mil 10 daga gabar tekun Hillsborough, amma yawanta ya ragu sosai daga makon da ya gabata.
An kuma ga ruwan sama mai tsananin zafi a yankin Pasco.
A makon da ya gabata an samu matsakaicin taro a cikin yankin Pinellas da ke kusa da shi, daga ƙananan zuwa manyan taro a cikin yankin bakin teku na Hillsborough County, manyan taro a cikin Manatee da Sarasota da yankunan bakin teku, matsakaicin taro a Charlotte County, babban taro a cikin yankin bakin teku na Lee County, da ƙananan taro a cikin Collier County.
A cikin yankunan Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee da Collier, har yanzu akwai yiwuwar ciwon ciwon huhu.
Ba a samu rahoton irin wannan a arewa maso yammacin Florida ba a makon da ya gabata.
